r of users and expanding variety of MMORPGs becoming available, and as a former Everquest player myself I have found it to be a convenient place to start. I am beginning by launching a questionnaire to all the Everquest-related sites I can find while doing literature-review on the topic. If you could take a few minutes to answer this questionnaire I would greatly appreciate it. Compiled results will be used confidentially, and you are free to omit any question you feel uncomfortable with. Of course, if you answered this questionnaire on another site please don’t answer it again <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Thanks!<br>
<br>
1.) How old are you?<br>
<br>
2.) Are you male or female?<br>
<br>
3.) Where do you live (nation/state/city)?<br>
<br>
4.) What race or ethnic group(s) do you identify with?<br>
<br>
4.) What is your occupation?<br>
<br>
5.) What is your average yearly income?<br>
<br>
6.) How long have you been playing Everquest?<br>
<br>
7.) Have you ever quit playing EQ for a period longer than 2 months? If so, why did you quite, for how long, and why did you return?<br>
<br>
8.) What are your character(s) class and level?<br>
<br>
9.) Do you belong to a guild? If so, what is the average member level? Does the guild have particular orientations (role-playing, raids, etc.)? Are you an officer or the guild leader of the guild?<br>
<br>
10.) Do you know people from the game in real life? How many and what is their relation to you (friends, family, fiancée, etc.)? Did you first meet them online or in real life?<br>
<br>
11.) What raid experience do you have (dungeon raids, dragon raids, plane raids, etc.)?<br>
<br>
12.) What server(s) do you play on?<br>
<br>
13.) Have you played any prior RPG orientated games (MUDs, CCGs, D&amp;D, etc.)?<br>
<br>
14.) What are your favorite things about EQ – why do you play?<br>
<br>
15.) Do you see yourself maintaining any of the relationships made in EQ beyond the game (perhaps across games, in real life, email, etc.)?<br>
<br>
16.) How many hours do you average per week playing EQ? How many hours per week in EQ related but not in-game activities (e.g. forums)?<br>
<br>
17.) How do you divide your time between grouping, soloing, and other activities (trade-skills, questing, buying/selling, etc.)? Do you tend to group with the same or different people? <br>
<br>
18.) What zones do you tend to spend the most time in (if any)?<br>
<br>
19.) Do you plan on playing EQ2 or other MMORPGs in the future?<br>
<br>
20.) Have you ever been to a Fan Faire? If so, describe the experience.<br>
<br>
Any other comments?<br>
<br>
